Before first release
====================

use Perl 6 built-in routines base(str) and parse-base(str) to simplify
  number base conversions [DONE]

add named param for upper case to base conversions [DONE]

add named param for leading code for non-decimal numbers ('0x', '0b') [DONE]

add in README.md that these subs are for uint numbers only [DONE]

Possible future features
========================

simpler interface to general transformation up to 36

bases higher than 36


